entry.

#####################50###########################
:PropsNewButton:$OPENWINHOME/bin/helpopen handbooks/binder.handbook
New

Click SELECT on New to create a new File Type 
entry.

:CutButton:$OPENWINHOME/bin/helpopen handbooks/binder.handbook
Cut

Click SELECT on Cut to remove the currently
selected File Type entry from the current Binder 
entry and move it to the clipboard.

#####################50###########################
:CopyButton:$OPENWINHOME/bin/helpopen handbooks/binder.handbook
Copy

Click SELECT on Copy to copy the currently
selected File Type entry to the clipboard.

:PasteButton:$OPENWINHOME/bin/helpopen handbooks/binder.handbook
